        "subject": "LU-14772 tests: remove conf-sanity ONLY_MINUTES skip",
        "message": "LU-14772 tests: remove conf-sanity ONLY_MINUTES skip\n\nDon't limit ONLY_MINUTES=1 in conf-sanity.sh, this was intended\nto be a short-term workaround while conf-sanity was being split.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=conf-sanity env=ONLY=1,ONLY_MINUTES=2\nFixes: 4a9fc7ceba (\"LU-14772 tests: Add conf-sanity-framework.sh\")\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Id09b0d6d3ea13bbab60923916606d7848e300c1e\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61427\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Chakshu Kansal <ckansal@ddn.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Vitaliy Kuznetsov <vkuznetsov@ddn.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
